{"tid":1331493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗區議會，約30名市民高叫反對區議會政治化","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:47:43.000Z","uid":22714,"like":2,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c5a774d36384a18a66bdb0e0fbc87bf6648e55","tid":1331493,"uid":22714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"深水埗區議會開會，其中一個議題是討論行政長官就修訂《逃犯條例》事件的回應。旁聽席上有市民多次打斷會議進程，深水埗區議會主席張永森，三度宣布休會，而最終由於未能召開會議，約早上10時宣布中止會議。由於有議員與市民發生口角爭執，有警員及救護員到場。<br />\n<br />\n區議會原定早上9時半開會，約30名市民手持「反暴力、反暴徒」的標語到場，<span style=\"color: red;\">高叫反對區議會政治化</span>，又表示希望解決區內劏房以及衞生問題，強調反暴力，還社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議員袁海文回應市民說，議會會討論民生議題，市民應讓議程順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469189-20190719.htm?share=twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469189-20190719.htm%3Fshare%3Dtwitter&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=df2a1aa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469189-20190719.htm%3Fshare%3Dtwitter&h=9c98f4aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469189-20190719.htm?share=twitter</a>"},{"pid":"b6e37c6f9303f81cc799596d93de1d5d1b917c4f","tid":1331493,"uid":247892,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"唔投建制佢地就會幫你根治民生問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0d9897ef4d16dc06e8fe512a659b3c6b79a2cf","tid":1331493,"uid":269578,"like":2,"dislike":54,"score":-52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"黃絲做乜，梁振英鬥爭系统就跟住照做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a0d3c662cbaaf41b5e5f43eb646a63e3565ca6","tid":1331493,"uid":277235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"re